**2b. Add `tool_progress` switch case (after `tool_call_delta` case, before `tool_call_end`)**

Insert a new case after the `tool_call_delta` case block (after line 213, before the `tool_call_end` case at line 215):

```typescript
      case 'tool_progress': {
        const tp = data as ToolProgressEvent;
        const existing = findToolCallPart(tp.toolCallId);
        if (existing) {
